      "text": "Tribalism and Belonging. A month later, in one of those visioning meetings, I was the white guy in the public meeting getting publicly shamed—and rightfully so. \"I tried to make a point about the challenges of being in the visible minority. That proved to be volatile coming from me (as The Rich White Male in the room).\" [https://dobbse.net/thinair/2009/05/tribalism-and-belonging.html blog]"
